Applying to upwork jobs has never been easy.

Proposi facilitates and speeds up the process of writing proposals and apply to upwork jobs; all you need to do is select a template -there are a lot of templates- and hit the apply button.

Proposi provides a ton of engaging,winning upwork proposals,that will help you  stand out and get a reply from the client.

Proposi allows you to save new proposals, edit the existing ones and customize them.

This extension is not a part of Upwork or endorsed by Upwork in any way.
